  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD & TWITTER</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Players will embark on a first-person experience in ArroGation: Unlight Of Day that is full of suspense, thrills, anD the unknown. You wiLl dElve into the abandoned village of Yunlin and confront the Specter that hideS in the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/fd969d07068c14e1f74fec3f646d984c.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/b566c777c8317c2e20e5d1560c4fcc64.avif?t=1677158174\" width=615 height=79 /></span><br><br>In this village shrouded in the darkness lurks a multitude of monsters you have never seen before, and their tragic experiences and resentments seem to be hidden beneath their frightening appearance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.poster.avif?t=1677158174\" width=614 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.webm?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/f0a764fd47c4bf188b6c6d30de94427d.mp4?t=1677158174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vid